Its easy to get around financial fair play for teams like City:

- Invest all your millions(billions?) in your youth academy and stadium. The stadium will increase revenue, and a top of the world youth academy will produce an endless supply of players

- Get the best scouts money can buy and send them all over the world to find cheap young talent. Fill up your youth academy with them and homegrown talent.

Admittedly this plan will take a few years to work. But when it does you will have a never ending supply of players to promote to your first team and/or send on loan where they will gain value to be sold on at a profit.

snippet.textDisplay:
Master has said:

“a Dafa disciple, or a cultivator, has no enemies. The only thing you have a role in is saving people, and you have nothing to do with using human means and human principles to punish or pronounce judgment on people. This is a fundamental issue!” (“Teaching the Fa in the City of Chicago,” Collected Fa Teachings, Vol VII)

Because people in China are facing a major disaster, it is Dafa disciples' inescapable responsibility to save them. During this process, some practitioners judge everyday people, such as so and so is not savable and so and so is so evil. Hidden in their judgments, they have already decided that this person should be eliminated. Such judgments come from our own notions and are not acknowledged by Dafa. We still have human notions, which limit our vision so that we cannot see through many things. But we are Dafa disciples, so our thoughts should not be influenced by everyday people's behaviors at the surface level or their behaviors at a certain moment. What we should do is to try our best to save people.

The Chinese people are in great danger. This is a chance for us to really display our mighty virtue and our selflessness. The Chinese have a saying: “One's true heart will be seen in disasters.” Our behaviors and the Communist Party's actions make an obvious contrast. Moreover, everybody is trying to save his own life now. So people would believe what we tell them as long as it may help to save them. So, at this crucial moment, more people will accept the truth of Dafa that we tell them.
